data.description: Welcome to your charming oasis! This delightful residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Nestled on a beautifully landscaped lot with an inviting home featuring three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms.Step inside to discover a warm and inviting interior, where natural light dances across the NEW main floor pergo style flooring. The heart of the home boasts a cozy living area, ideal for relaxation or entertaining guests. The kitchen adjoining the dining room are complete with modern appliances and stylish cabinetry. Retreat to the tranquil living quarters located on the upper level, a serene sanctuary offering a private haven to unwind after a long day. Venture outside to discover your own private paradise. The expansive yard is a lush retreat, perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply soaking up the sunshine, offering plenty of privacy with the NEW fence. Whether you're hosting a barbecue with friends or enjoying a quiet morning coffee, this backyard oasis offers endless possibilities for enjoyment and relaxation. Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining, this home offers the perfect balance for it's new owners.
